extends staycleanLayout.pug
block links
  link(rel='stylesheet', href='scleanMain.css')
block content
  // About Us section
  .container-fluid.bg-grey(style='padding:60px 80px;')
    .row
      .col-sm-12
        h2(style='margin-bottom: 20px;') Who We Are
        ul
          li
            | Stay Clean is the 
            strong leading provider 
            | of residential and commercial waste management services in Uganda.
            i.fas.fa-medal(style='margin-left:20px; font-size:40px;')
          br
          li
            | Our purpose is to 
            strong empower communities
            |  to keep the environments they live in healthy and happy.
            i.fas.fa-hand-sparkles(style='margin-left:60px; font-size:40px;')
          br
          li
            | Our 350 employees serve around 
            strong 250,000 
            | households, in 20 major towns and cities across Uganda.
            i.fas.fa-globe-africa(style='margin-left:60px; font-size:40px;')
          br
  .container-fluid.bg-light-blue
    .row
      .col-sm-4
        img(src='images/garbage_truck4.jpeg')
      .col-sm-8
        h2 Our Mission &amp; Values
        p
          | Our mission at Safe Clean is to provide reliable automated waste management services to communities.
          | Our team goes over and above to provide an exceptional service. Our solutions can be tailored to meet specific community
          | needs so if you don&apos;t see what you are looking for, call us to learn more.
  // Team section
  .container-fluid(style='padding: 30px 30px;')
    h2(style='margin-left: 480px;') Our Team
    .row
      .column
        .card
          img.mx-auto.d-block(src='images/Founder1.jpeg', alt='Victoria', style='width:300px; height:300px; object-fit: cover; padding: 15px 0px 5px 0px;')
          .container
            h4(style='text-align: center;') Victoria Magaiga
            p.title CEO &amp; Founder
            p
              | Jane is the chief executive officer of Safe Clean and a member of the Board of Directors.
              | Prior to her current role, she held several key positions within the service sector, including as senior vice president
              | and director of financial planning and analysis at GSX Services.
      .column
        .card
          img.mx-auto.d-block(src='images/Founder2.jpeg', alt='Martin', style='width:300px; height:300px; object-fit: cover; padding: 15px 0px 5px 0px;')
          .container
            h4(style='text-align: center;') Martin Kamulegeya
            p.title COO
            p
              | As chief operating officer (COO) for Safe Clean, Martin is reponsible for field operations, including oversight
              | of collections and disposals, recycling and landfills. He joined Safe Clean from Waste-Plus - Kenya where he worked for 3 years
              | as the market area manager.
      .column
        .card
          img.mx-auto.d-block(src='images/Founder3.jpeg', alt='Bernice', style='width:300px; height:300px; object-fit: cover; padding: 15px 0px 5px 0px;')
          .container
            h4(style='text-align: center;') Bernice Ssempebwa
            p.title CFO
            p
              | Bernice is our new executive vice presdient and chief financial officer for Safe Clean, responsible for all finance functions. Since joining the company in 2019
              | she has held several positions including assistant treasurer and senior audit manager.
  // Footer section
  footer.container-fluid.bg-light-blue.text-center(style='padding: 5px;')
    p
      | &copy; 
      a(href='/main', style='color: rgb(187, 204, 236); font-size: 15px; text-align: center;') 2021 Stay Clean
